{"tid":2455810,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公民黨明再開會商前路","createTime":"2021-03-21T11:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T13:17:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cf47b816a28a477011a05a71e82acc60e8e6e3cf","tid":2455810,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T11:49:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210321/5VHONZLDJ5C6XPCJHWE24GKTOY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210321%2F5VHONZLDJ5C6XPCJHWE24GKTOY%2F&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=95fa5158\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210321%2F5VHONZLDJ5C6XPCJHWE24GKTOY%2F&h=2948b84f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210321/5VHONZLDJ5C6XPCJHWE24GKTOY/</a><br />\n<br />\n公民黨明再開會商前路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ul8x4CtaP-tXvMy_Ckf_3yPp_FA=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/X3HHZT5ZERFLNNJR2RPDQWSBHM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUl8x4CtaP-tXvMy_Ckf_3yPp_FA%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FX3HHZT5ZERFLNNJR2RPDQWSBHM.jpg&h=71a52919&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■公民黨昨舉行退修會商討未來路向，主席梁家傑與會後離開。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】四位公民黨前成員包括楊岳橋、譚文豪、郭家麒、李予信，被控顛覆國家政權，三人仍還柙，公民黨前景堪憂，該黨昨舉行退修會討論區議員宣誓、未來發展方向如會否再派員參選等。據悉，會上未有任何決定，但該黨執委會將於明日開會，考慮如何與黨員一齊決定黨的未來路向，現階段不排除任何選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有黨員強調不會解散<br />\n<br />\n公民黨副主席賴仁彪完會後表示，會上黨員主要討論區議員宣誓問題、公民黨在目前政治環境下應如何自處這兩大方向，強調昨日退修會是以交流意見、了解黨員意見為主，以「自由討論、由下而上」的方式議事。<br />\n<br />\n有公民黨中人透露，昨日的退修會上主要讓黨員發表意見，沒有任何「決定」公佈。公民黨下周一會再召開執委會，決定應如何與黨員一同決定公民黨的去向，而公民黨的去向則可以有各種各樣的可能，有人就強調公民黨不會解散。<br />\n<br />\n以「四十五條關注組成員」為骨幹的公民黨2006年創黨至今15年，創黨成員包括湯家驊、吳靄儀、梁家傑、張超雄、譚香文等。......................................<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/msyjbNxwVCGIwjGiDbyz9xbWoAc=/802x534/filters:quality\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmsyjbNxwVCGIwjGiDbyz9xbWoAc%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=56953534\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmsyjbNxwVCGIwjGiDbyz9xbWoAc%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality&h=45566bb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/msyjbNxwVCGIwjGiDbyz9xbWoAc=/802x534/filters:quality</a>(100)/<a href=\"http://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F2TDHGECYJAZNIMWTOA6IQC334.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF2TDHGECYJAZNIMWTOA6IQC334.jpg&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=becec9cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F2TDHGECYJAZNIMWTOA6IQC334.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"0e93734db68b75a806bcc1507cfbe9d075e5f84c","tid":2455810,"uid":84037,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:44:16.000Z","msg":"算鳩數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4ce441a4790a47d19a172fedcd711441badf6a","tid":2455810,"uid":45035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:52:32.000Z","msg":"有險可守"},{"pid":"479f3e31e06a984b2445c0850642a58fe8ca32d2","tid":2455810,"uid":106084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:54:56.000Z","msg":"執七咗去啦"},{"pid":"915eb3d9527d2a1123cc13cdde91504f75a90ca8","tid":2455810,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:09:41.000Z","msg":"係香港搞政治 晒鳩氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d39454c4738c45b280c76e9e977bb56ecb634f","tid":2455810,